{"tid":564343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"背部紋「好人」二字　廣西漢街頭搶劫被逮","createTime":"2018-02-18T01:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T08:15:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"05ec31f3a4f82901184f1e10d43446dbce0152b4","tid":564343,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T01:19:52.000Z","msg":"02月18日(日) 06:41   <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180218/photo/bkncn-20180218064142013-0218_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180218064335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180218%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180218064142013-0218_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180218064335&h=0b072625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子背部紋有「好人」二字。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n廣西防城港三名男子在街頭向一名女子搶劫，結果被警方逮捕。令意想不到的是，警方對三人身體檢查時，發現其中一人的背部紋了「好人」二字。 <br />\n<br />\n該名疑犯自稱，幾年前，他在後背紋上「好人」二字，是立志要做個好人。但近兩個月來一直沒找到工作，沒錢給女兒買奶粉，在兩名同鄉的慫恿下，於是搶劫。 <br />\n<br />\n該名疑犯事後表示很後悔，「因為意志不堅定，對不起背上的兩個字，對不起家人！」"},{"pid":"9f10257c71950c859d970a471c153a3fe72f55bb","tid":564343,"uid":1067,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T01:23:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我不是</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好人</span>tee.jpg"},{"pid":"6b9ca1e9751b69eb909e5f82a775ba8122e7dd9b","tid":564343,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T01:36:45.000Z","msg":"過年都要去搶野，究竟有幾大苦衷？"},{"pid":"009eb60c7182d28ece70c73a42f528bedc42e4d3","tid":564343,"uid":18948,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6b9ca1e9751b69eb909e5f82a775ba8122e7dd9b","tid":564343,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T01:36:45.000Z","msg":"過年都要去搶野，究竟有幾大苦衷？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T02:08:21.000Z","msg":"兩個月來一直沒找到工作，沒錢給女兒買奶粉"},{"pid":"0aeb6764d3bf8a34ea4a4660342945b51c08bf25","tid":564343,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T02:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa